Package: downscaleLST.MDV
Title: Downscaling Land Surface Temperature for the Antarctic Dry Valleys
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Maite",
           family = "Lezama Valdes",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "maite.lezama@uni-muenster.de")
Description: This package enables users to downscale MOD/MYD11_L2 scenes
    for daytime hours within the McMurdo Dry Valleys, Antarctica to a 30m
    spatial resolution
